<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00">哎呀，<tag a="110" b="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我有件猶豫的事，<delay20 />
能不能找你商量一下呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道你……<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有沒有考慮過，<delay20 />
要離開這座島？<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像我啊，<delay8 />就還有很多想知道、<delay8 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想親眼見識的事物呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以我<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />正在考慮
要不要搬去別座島呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">不要走！</message>
	<message label="001_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我覺得很好啊</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay8 />真巧呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我正好想跟你說一件事。<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然很突然，<delay8 />
但是我已經<delay8 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />決定要搬出這座島了。<pageBreak /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />你不要誤會喔<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我可不是對<tag a="110" b="33" /><delay8 />
有什麼不滿才想搬走的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是也開始想看看外面的世界了。<10_4 />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />該怎麼說呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我希望自己<delay8 />能不斷吸收新知識嘛！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我不希望你走！</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">加油！</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 01 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真抱歉，剛才沒注意到你。<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我正在想事情……<pageBreak />我問你喔，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />。<delay20 />
如果我說我要離開這座島，<delay8 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你會怎麼樣呢？<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />對不起，說了些讓你誤會的話，<delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是，<delay8 />我現在其實很迷惘……<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到底是該追求改變，還是選擇穩定的生活<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你覺得呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">留在這裡嘛！</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">一路順風</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />難道<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
你是在挽留我嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你說的也對……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然這裡還有人需要我，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就不應該離開這座島上。<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我決定不搬家了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且，<delay20 />其實我很高興聽到你這麼說呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />謝謝你願意聽我訴說煩惱，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望我留在這座島上嗎？<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我<delay8 />只想到自己，<delay20 />
好像完全沒有顧慮到<delay8 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那些關心我的人呢……<pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我明白了，<delay20 /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們別談搬家的事情了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從今以後，<delay8 />
我依然是這座島上的居民喔！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />被你這麼一說，我覺得想搬家的自己<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />簡直是丟了<tag a="110" b="15" />的臉！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我決定不搬家了！<delay8 />不搬了！<delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從今以後，<delay20 />我依然是
<tag a="110" b="33" />的居民喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這段時間真是受你照顧了呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果說我沒有留戀，<delay8 />
那肯定是騙人的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<delay8 />為了我自己的將來，<delay20 />
還是要努力邁出新的一步才行！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我們彼此互相勉勵吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就知道<delay8 />你會這麼說呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別擔心，在這座島上的回憶，<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定都會成為我的力量。<delay frames="40" />
所以<delay8 /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就算我搬到別的地方也不要緊！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
謝謝你至今以來對我的照顧，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望你別忘了我喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">說不定，<delay8 />我其實一直在等誰<delay8 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />從背後推我一把呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想那個人肯定就是你吧。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我就要離開這座島了，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但是<tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我絕對不會忘記你的！<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
